VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT automountServiceAccountToken\s*:\s*true
WHEN EXPR MISSING:automountServiceAccountToken:\s*false && PRESENT:kind:\s*Deployment|kind:\s*StatefulSet|kind:\s*Pod|kind:\s*DaemonSet
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects pods or service accounts with automatic service account token mounting enabled.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Default Service Account Token Auto-Mounted.
